I understand the
outcome is upsetting.

22
00:03:24,610 --> 00:03:28,444
However, results are results.

23
00:03:28,477 --> 00:03:31,510
No matter how much
sorrow there may be,

24
00:03:31,544 --> 00:03:35,244
