yourself like this.

120
00:13:17,492 --> 00:13:20,892
Tokiko, take care of yourself.

121
00:13:20,926 --> 00:13:23,826
-N-- Next.

122
00:13:23,859 --> 00:13:24,792
-Tokiko.

123
00:13:24,826 --> 00:13:25,292
Tokiko.

124
