To be honest, I can't
stand seeing you like this.

125
00:13:41,459 --> 00:13:45,092
Please, cheer up.

126
00:13:45,126 --> 00:13:47,826
Whatever it takes,
I'll do anything just

127
00:13:47,859 --> 00:13:49,126
to see smile again.

128
00:13:53,026 --> 00:13:53,492
Tokiko.

129
00:13:57,159 --> 00:13:59,626
-Thanks, Gota, but--

130
00:14:26,259 --> 00:14:27,326
TOKIKO (VOICEOVER): Kazuki.

131
00:14:54,226 --> 00:14:56,992
What can I do for you?

132
00:15:14,659 --> 00:15:17,926
-Eventually, I'll settle things
with you once and for all.

133
00:15:17,959 --> 00:15:21,359
Until I do, I won't be able to
be myself and truly take off.

134
00:15:21,392 --> 00:15:21,859
-Chouno.

135
00:15:24,892 --> 00:15:27,692
I also plan to settle things
with you once and for all.

136
00:15:34,592 --> 00:15:35,526
-I will settle it.

137
00:15:38,426 --> 00:15:40,659
-How are the missions
in other areas going?

138
00:15:40,692 --> 00:15:42,692
-50% are complete.

139
00:15:42,726 --> 00:15:44,992
The rest are in progress.

140
00:15:45,026 --> 00:15:47,159
We are currently
working on bringing

141
00:15:47,192 --> 00:15:49,459
every confirmed homunculi
under our control.

142
00:15:49,492 --> 00:15:51,192
-Followed by a
gradual suspension

143
00:15:51,226 --> 00:15:53,292
of all alchemist army activity?

144
00:15:53,326 --> 00:15:54,959
Are you serious about that?

145
00:15:54,992 --> 00:15:56,326
-Yes.

146
00:15:56,359 --> 00:15:58,992
I've been having meetings with
armies from various nations.

147
00:15:59,026 --> 00:16:01,426
