years since alchemy began

148
00:16:01,459 --> 00:16:03,659
and the completion of
the philosopher's stone

149
00:16:03,692 --> 00:16:05,592
is still far away.

150
00:16:05,626 --> 00:16:08,526
In addition, we've not been
able to properly utilize

151
00:16:08,559 --> 00:16:11,826
the power we currently have and
we continue to make mistakes.

152
00:16:11,859 --> 00:16:15,226
I believe it is time for us to
take a step back and reexamine

153
00:16:15,259 --> 00:16:16,992
our progress thus far.

154
00:16:17,026 --> 00:16:19,092
-Is that even
possible right now?

155
00:16:19,126 --> 00:16:23,092
-Whether it's possible
or not, it must be done.

156
00:16:23,126 --> 00:16:25,759
It's the least we
can do for those

157
00:16:25,792 --> 00:16:29,626
two warriors up on the moon.

158
00:16:29,659 --> 00:16:31,159
-Great Warrior Chief.

159
00:16:31,192 --> 00:16:34,992
-Warrior Tokiko, what is it?

160
00:16:35,026 --> 00:16:37,826
-Great Warrior Chief,
I have a request.

161
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:17,992
-Tokiko, I heard.

162
00:17:25,226 --> 00:17:28,892
I know about your final mission
to take care of Papillon.

163
00:17:28,926 --> 00:17:30,792
You can count me in.

164
00:17:46,226 --> 00:17:47,826
-Hey, come on, you
guys are so slow.

165
00:17:47,859 --> 00:17:49,926
What the heck took you so long?

166
00:17:49,959 --> 00:17:51,626
I was getting tired of waiting.

167
00:17:51,659 --> 00:17:53,826
-We heard about what you
guys are planning to do.

168
00:17:53,859 --> 00:17:56,792
-And we won't let
you do this alone.

169
00:17:56,826 --> 00:17:57,892
-That's right, Tokiko.

170
00:17:57,926 --> 00:17:59,859
