184
00:18:52,992 --> 00:18:54,959
-I'm aware of that.

185
00:18:54,992 --> 00:18:55,692
Let's go.

186
00:19:07,892 --> 00:19:11,992
-Hm, if you're going to watch
the moon, do it someplace else.

187
00:19:12,026 --> 00:19:14,859
