eat, eat somewhere else.

188
00:19:14,892 --> 00:19:15,726
-Want some?

189
00:19:15,759 --> 00:19:16,992
It's my Mama.

190
00:19:17,026 --> 00:19:19,659
Well, actually, it's the
remains of her failed attempt

191
00:19:19,692 --> 00:19:21,692
to clone herself.

192
00:19:21,726 --> 00:19:23,792
-It doesn't even
wet my appetite.

193
00:19:23,826 --> 00:19:25,559
-Strange that you say that.

194
00:19:25,592 --> 00:19:28,926
