for close to 100 years.

195
00:19:28,959 --> 00:19:31,959
I'd heard that you didn't have
any urges for cannibalism.

196
00:19:31,992 --> 00:19:34,292
I guess it's true then huh?

197
00:19:34,326 --> 00:19:37,392
The reason a homunculus
has the urge to eat humans,

198
00:19:37,426 --> 00:19:39,592
some researchers
say it's attributed

199
00:19:39,626 --> 00:19:41,926
to an instinctive attachment.

200
00:19:41,959 --> 00:19:44,159
In other words,
it's like a desire

201
00:19:44,192 --> 00:19:48,359
to regain the human elements
that it had originally lost.

202
00:19:48,392 --> 00:19:50,859
You don't have any
attachments to human elements,

203
00:19:50,892 --> 00:19:53,326
to the human world,
or to society.

204
00:19:53,359 --> 00:19:55,926
As a homunculus
you are incomplete,

205
00:19:55,959 --> 00:19:58,326
but you've accomplished
what other homunculi haven't

206
00:19:58,359 --> 00:20:02,126
been able to do, breaking
away from being human.

207
00:20:02,159 --> 00:20:03,726
You are something
completely new that's

208
00:20:03,759 --> 00:20:05,826
neither human nor homunculus.

209
00:20:05,859 --> 00:20:08,492
