be a superhuman.

210
00:20:08,526 --> 00:20:11,492
-Go and speak your
nonsense someplace else.

211
00:20:11,526 --> 00:20:12,759
-You're right.

212
00:20:12,792 --> 00:20:15,926
This conversation is probably
nonsense to you and me,

213
00:20:15,959 --> 00:20:19,026
but I will tell you something
relevant for your own good.

214
00:20:19,059 --> 00:20:21,492
The alchemist warriors
are already nearby.

215
00:20:21,526 --> 00:20:22,926
