welcome for unwanted visitors.

218
00:20:32,826 --> 00:20:34,726
-Long time no see.

219
00:20:34,759 --> 00:20:37,792
-You really did it, didn't you?

220
00:20:37,826 --> 00:20:39,426
-The time has come for revenge.

221
00:20:39,459 --> 00:20:43,326
-Don't even think you're
going to get past here.

222
00:20:43,359 --> 00:20:46,192
-Animal type homunculike
created by Papillon.

223
00:20:46,226 --> 00:20:49,092
-Did he recreate them with
Dr. Alexandria's cloning

224
00:20:49,126 --> 00:20:49,926
technology?

225
00:20:49,959 --> 00:20:51,259
-That confirms it.

226
00:20:51,292 --> 00:20:53,792
There's no doubt Papillon
was on the other side.

227
00:20:56,859 --> 00:20:59,559
Let's go.

228
00:20:59,592 --> 00:21:00,959
-Buso renkin of archery.

229
00:21:04,859 --> 00:21:07,726
-Buso renkin of Katana sword.

230
00:21:07,759 --> 00:21:12,259
Sword Samurai X.

231
00:21:12,292 --> 00:21:17,159
-Buso renkin of
chakram, motor gear.

