-Clones.

239
00:21:40,159 --> 00:21:41,559
-Go on ahead, Tokiko.

240
00:21:41,592 --> 00:21:45,092
-I don't think so.

241
00:21:45,126 --> 00:21:47,126
-Tokiko, go ahead.

242
00:21:56,892 --> 00:21:59,292
-So what do you want?

243
00:21:59,326 --> 00:22:02,492
